body_html: Hi there, when I used audio_ops.audio_spectrogram() and contrib.signal.stft() for generating MFCCs, I found that the one using audio_ops is faster than the contrib.signal one. Do you have the same feeling? And do you plan to improve contrib.signal? Thanks a lot!

body: Hi there, when I used ``audio_ops.audio_spectrogram()`` and ``contrib.signal.stft()`` for generating MFCCs, I found that the one using ``audio_ops`` is faster than the ``contrib.signal`` one. Do you have the same feeling? And do you plan to improve contrib.signal? Thanks a lot!
